            english: "This month I will keep seeing the thinness through her skin. Behind my back, she will go ask the Gamma families for scraps. I will pretend I know nothing. Even so, we will remain hungry. I eat too much because I am sixteen and still growing; Eo lies and says she has never had much of an appetite."
